&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I used &lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;ceoloide&#x2F;ergogen-footprints&#x2F;tree&#x2F;main&quot;&gt;Ceoloide’s&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; footprint for the switch footprints, which are reversible, meaning that both halves of the board can use the same PCB design.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;

	&lt;img class=&quot;
			
			
			
			no-hover
                        
